  "detailed_description": "<h1>Limited Edition Boxsets</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116660/extras/1195775f57f88a94458ff0a30397a58d.avif?t=1596764938\" width=598 height=328 /></span><br><br>We have limited edition boxsets that we are making for our game release.  To get on the list visit our Skyride Studios website.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>ABOUT:<br><br>The year is 2048.  A virus known as \"Neon Tide\" spreads throughout robots in an unknown fashion.  It's your job to unlock the cause of the virus and find a way to stop it.<br><br>FEATURES:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Neon Tide is a visual novel where you explore a cyberpunk style world as three characters;</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116660/extras/d497f68c70a67ba586d10eb9d9ab7570.avif?t=1596764938\" width=300 height=816 /></span><br>Beta (a hologram who wishes he were human)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116660/extras/1b6ddc5d640ab36728d053ea03d0959e.avif?t=1596764938\" width=245 height=815 /></span><br>Lucy (an affected robot who fights for the equality of her race)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116660/extras/f972a3a16cbf158eff022e7a7436d04b.avif?t=1596764938\" width=266 height=816 /></span><br>Victoria (an affected robot who wants humans and robots to co-exist together)<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every choice you make in the game affects the story and each choice comes with a consequence.<br></li><li>One ending</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Full sound effects and music, we recommend playing with headphones.<br></li><li>Directed by Will Novy<br></li><li>Sound Design and Music by: Daemoneyeddeath</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "ABOUT:<br><br>The year is 2048.  A virus known as \"Neon Tide\" spreads throughout robots in an unknown fashion.  It's your job to unlock the cause of the virus and find a way to stop it.<br><br>FEATURES:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Neon Tide is a visual novel where you explore a cyberpunk style world as three characters;</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116660/extras/d497f68c70a67ba586d10eb9d9ab7570.avif?t=1596764938\" width=300 height=816 /></span><br>Beta (a hologram who wishes he were human)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116660/extras/1b6ddc5d640ab36728d053ea03d0959e.avif?t=1596764938\" width=245 height=815 /></span><br>Lucy (an affected robot who fights for the equality of her race)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116660/extras/f972a3a16cbf158eff022e7a7436d04b.avif?t=1596764938\" width=266 height=816 /></span><br>Victoria (an affected robot who wants humans and robots to co-exist together)<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every choice you make in the game affects the story and each choice comes with a consequence.<br></li><li>One ending</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Full sound effects and music, we recommend playing with headphones.<br></li><li>Directed by Will Novy<br></li><li>Sound Design and Music by: Daemoneyeddeath</li></ul>",
